public class CashReceiptInitiatorDerivedRoleTypeServiceImpl
extends org.kuali.rice.kim.service.support.impl.KimDerivedRoleTypeServiceBase

A role which determines membership in role for people who can initiate Cash Receipts. Members are those users which belong to KFS-SYS User but NOT KFS-FP Cash Manager.
